dcterms:description: The principal dataset used in this study comprises 230 Raman spectra of solvents and solvent mixtures, created from a set of 25 solvents. It includes pure samples as well as a non-exhaustive selection of 2, 3, 4, and 5 solvent mixtures, all labeled as to whether the sample contains a chlorinated solvent or not.
dcterms:title: Principal Dataset

dcterms:creator: S. B. Engelsen
dcterms:description: An additional dataset comprising 24 Raman spectra of carbohydrates was compiled for use as examples of possible outlier data, representing a class of substances distinct from the training dataset of solvents.
dcterms:title: Outlier Dataset

dcterms:creator: S. S. Khan
M. G. Madden
dcterms:description: UCI Datasets are mentioned in the context of one-class classification, providing a variety of datasets for testing classification techniques.
dcterms:title: UCI Datasets
